						<summary>

						<p>States that one <hi rend="bold">Kommama</hi> built the temple of Mādhavadēva in the village of <hi rend="bold">Peruvali</hi> and that her son made a gift of land for <hi rend="italic">naivēdyam</hi> to the said deity.</p>						

